snippet.textDisplay: There’s a certain sort of student of English that carries this book around like an emblem of honour, as if to understand the Middle English language confers an intellectual prestige beyond most people. Well, judging by this trailer, that type will not like this film. It’s immediately accessible and provocative. It is strange to see something so old (in the European context) appear to evoke some of the terror of its time. Surprisingly, I am looking forward to this film, based on this trailer, which is all the more surprising for a poem, which I thought inaccessible and elitist for most of my life.

snippet.textDisplay:
European Falun Dafa practitioners went to several high schools during the past several weeks. They introduced to students and teachers a meditation whose practitioners follow the principles of Truthfulness-Compassion-Forbearance.

Italy

Students watch the introductory video presented by Falun Dafa at the Accademia Leonardo Italian Language School.

Liceo Statale T. L.Caro - Liceo Linguistico is one of the best language high schools in Salerno, Southern Italy. Its renowned academic performance attracts many talented students from nearby regions. In recent years, students have heard about traditional Chinese culture, and the damage done by the Chinese Communist Party (CCP) during recent decades. Falun Dafa informational materials were also provided to all of the students.


Students learning the Falun Dafa exercise movements

Practitioners gave an exercise demonstration to some students on January 30, 2020. They shared their personal stories of physical benefits and moral improvement, and answered questions.

I hope hope hope that this will be a telling of Sir Gawain and the Green Knight that I tried to read in Middle English in Snordum's SFSC class in Middle and Old English. I wasn't terribly successful.
